# Write to main repo

- **Path**: Use the **main repository** for all file edits and new files:  
  **`/Users/edu/Documents/Code/Timbre-Audio-to-Brief/`**
- When editing or creating any project file, use that path (e.g. `/Users/edu/Documents/Code/Timbre-Audio-to-Brief/download_songs_v2.py`, not a worktree path like `.../worktrees/.../xqe/download_songs_v2.py`).
- This ensures changes always land in the main repo where you run scripts (e.g. `download_songs_v2.py`) and where `main` is checked out for git.
